## âš™ï¸ Technologies Used

- **Node.js** + **Express.js**
- **MongoDB** (via Mongoose)
- **Stripe API** (secure payments)
- **Socket.IO** (real-time per-order chat)
- **dotenv**, **CORS**, **body-parser**, etc.
- **Hosted on** Render or Railway

